{"title":"胜利之本是兵民——忆敌后抗战","authors":["萧华"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":8,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利之本是兵民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——忆敌后抗战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗战胜利二十春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦岁月记犹新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本强盗伸魔爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半壁河山被鲸吞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城乡为墟尸遍野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国恨家仇似海深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祸国殃民国民党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外战外行当逃兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安圣地如灯塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席思想是南针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"持久抗战号角响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片红旗出雁门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河怒涛连天涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江两岸聚风云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平型关下歼板垣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳明堡前敌机焚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力挽狂澜作砥柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我军威名中外闻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄师挺进沦陷区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利剑万把插敌心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创建敌后根据地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利之本是兵民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减租减息政策好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民合作鱼水亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送信带路递情报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献粮参军出战勤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村都是游击队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山皆有主力军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖荡出没武工队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原驰骋轻骑兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青纱帐里枪声紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野大摆地雷阵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路公路节节断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深沟高垒化烟尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击战略战术巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面围困侵略军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地方武装和民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"配合主力杀敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗日英雄千百万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气壮山河志凌云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎“扫荡”和“清剿”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙铁壁谁能侵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整风运动大开展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全党团结一条心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜困难向前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年愈战愈坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破黑暗迎曙光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏军打败希特勒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我军反攻势难挡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗高插长白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战马痛饮鸭绿江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月三日鸣鞭炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里河山庆重光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民欢呼毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举国歌颂共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导抗战获胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导人民求解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日南天烽火急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国强盗逞凶狂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中越人民好兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同仇敌忾歼豺狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"援越抗美怒潮起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雷震荡太平洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝自跳火山口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找得南越好坟场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看二十年前事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东条覆败是榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民战争必胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义定灭亡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年八月十五日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}